@page "/about"

<MudContainer Class="px-0 pb-4">
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h4">About D'Orc</MudText>

    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
        D'Orc is a free and open-source web application that provides useful tools for pen-and-paper roleplaying,
        both online and offline.<br>
        Check out the GitHub project page here: <a href="https://github.com/Phoenox/dorc">github.com/Phoenox/dorc</a>
    </MudText>
</MudContainer>

